28 SUMMARY
2299 This amendment makes the following changes to the bill.
30 1. It changes the title.
31 2. It adds language to allow the fish hatchery maintenance fund to be used for overtime
32 personnel services costs when overtime for fish stocking and other hatchery-related work
33 is operationally required and also makes clear that the fund may support the design,
34 construction and operation of additional state fish hatcheries.
35 3. It establishes the Inland Fisheries Conservation and Enhancement Program, which
36 replaces the Inland Fisheries Conservation and Enhancement Fund established in the bill,
37 and establishes program requirements and duties.
Page 4 - 132LR0251(02)
